data.description: Views from every angle. This beautiful 3 bedroom home has the space you need for your family. The open layout makes entertaining a breeze. The bedrooms are spacious and there's an office area that could be transformed into another bedroom. Through the breezeway is a large room over the garage perfect for watching the big game. The acreage has space for your animals with approximately 7 acres fenced in already. Enjoy your morning coffee on the back deck. And don't forget the in-ground salt water pool! You will be the 'go to' hang out spot for family and friends. Don't let this one slip away. Call today!  (Property is being sold AS IS and your inspections are welcome.)
